<HEAD>President Announces New Anti-Corruption Drive</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LAGOS, Nigeria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Nigeria's military leader on Wednesday
announced a new campaign aimed at weeding out corrupt officials in
